productBaseInfoV1.title: Cowon EH2 High-Tech Hybrid Earphone Wired Headphones(Red, In the Ear)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Cowon EH2 employs luxurious metal to embody modern minimalism. The simplistic straight lines, gently curving corners and sophisticated grid pattern offer a sense of sophistication. The red fabric cable offers a warm sense of luxury and its combination with the metallic material tops off the sensual elegance of this premium product. An exclusive cord stopper eliminates tangles and sets position where the cords diverge. The high-end EH2 is hassle-free and is outfitted with dust filters for protection while delivering true-to-life sound. The included dust brush keeps Cowon EH2 in clean condition with ease, regardless of the environment. The 24K gold plated plug minimizes contact resistance, signal interference and noise to deliver true Hi-Fi sound. Cowon's commitment to quality to high-end audio devices still goes with Cowon EH2. The flexible braided cable minimizes touch noises that can be annoying when listening on the move. The fabric cable prevents tangling and is strong enough to eliminate concerns about disconnection. Listening to music in a library-quite room or the noisy outdoors requires the comfort and noise isolation of the four, high-end dual-structure noise isolation ear caps with foam tips and the four silicon ear caps. The urethane foam tip, an essential accessory for in-ear earphones, is made with ultra-high-end material that ensures a superb fit and perfect seal for vivid sound yet comfortable wear even for extended listening sessions. Choose from among the nice kinds of ear caps, including silicon ear caps which can be used anytime conveniently, for customized comfort and professional performance. For accurate transmission of true-to-life Hi-Fi sound, Cowon EH2 employs a metal housing to dampen vibration and an internal environment that is acoustically designed and engineered for the utmost in sound production. The luxuriously smooth, eye cataching metal body is durable. It's professional finish and smooth surface are sure to please everybody. The harmony between a Balanced Armature Driver and a Dynamic Driver delivers flat and undistorted sound even in a wide range of sound frequencies from 20Hz to 22, 000Hz. Enjoy the best in all genres of music! Cowon EH2 produces reference-level sound from quite classical pieces and delicate jazz. Refreshingly clear vocals get rid of any stuffiness and the stunning resolution deliver a whole new level of sound when listening to band or orchestral music. Supported by a balanced Armature Driver, the dynamic driver expertly tuned for a natural-sounding range delivers robust and majestic mid-bass. Cowon EH2 offers a new level of listening pleasure from today's bass-heavy tracks. The balanced Armature Driver for detailed high sounds and the Dynamic Driver for magnificent bass sounds are delicately combined with unique and intricate Cowon tuning technology to deliver the utmost in sound fidelity. Cowon EH2 includes tweeter and woofer structure adopted in high-end Hi-Fi audio systems to produce true-to-life, exquisitely balanced sound-nothing less will do. The premium sounds emanating from Cowon EH2 are the result of the Balanced Armature Driver, a unit that is voiced for the highest level of resolution possible today, with the Dynamic Driver tuned for analog feel with the artful touch of Cowon's signature acoustic tuning. With exceptional clarity and resolution, Cowon EH2's uncompromisingly clear high and medium sounds are unrivaled in its class. Cowon's attention to detail lets listeners experience the subtle tremor of snare drum and even the performer's breathing for the highest standards in auditory enjoyment. Cowon EH2 strikes the optimum balance between firm and dense bass response and clear high and medium tones. Both vocals and musical performances are artfully achieved through Cowon's acoustic tuning technology that ensures distortion-free sounds from both right and left channels.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Sennheiser PX 200-II Wired Headphones(Black, On the Ear)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Sennheiser has loaded PX 200-II Headphone with some of the best audio enhancing features that efficiently complements its top-notch build quality. The on-the-ear design has been incorporated keeping in mind the usability and comfort factor that gains prominence especially when it comes to extended periods of use. The supra-aural ear cups are backed by the over-the-head design for a secure fit that does not fall out when you move your head. This Sennheiser headphone operates on wired connectivity with range compatible audio sources. Design This headphone has been well-constructed to inculcate the best features that enhance the overall comfort level. The supra-aural ear cups of this headphone come fitted with soft leatherette ear pads on the inner side to rest comfortably on your ears without annoying you. The open back of the ear cups are meant for creating a lifelike listening experience. These ear cups are attached to a headband that sits along the contours of your head to exert a balanced force for a perfect-fit. The fold and flip design of the PX 200-II Headphone is meant to enhance its overall portability. You can turn the ear cups at 90 degrees for those moments when you want to enjoy music without wearing it. Additionally, you can fold the headphones towards the headband and moreover you can conveniently lock it in open and closed position. This headphone comes fitted with a 1.2 m long single-sided cable that houses an integrated volume control to let you adjust the loudness without digging out for the audio source. The 3.5 mm audio plug that this headphone features makes this headphone compatible with a range of devices including MP3 players, iPods, iPhones and other portable media players. Sound This Sennheiser headphone is highly efficient in producing and reflecting clear and crisp sound without any distortion. The 32 ohm of impedance of this device helps it to maintain optimum level of loudness for better audibility. The efficiency of this device gets a resounding boost from 115 dB/mW of sensitivity. Also, each and every beat present in the original track gets apt representation in the sound produced as this device has frequency response of 10 Hz to 21000 Hz.

Other Features: Single-sided Cable, Optimised for MP3, iPod, iPhone, Portable Media Players

productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The Glass Screen Protector for the from mobile ka amrit has been specially made with scratch resistant material with more precise fit. Due to the 0.23mm thickness and surface hardness of 8~9H the Glass Screen Protector provides premium protection and without any loss in touch screen sensitivity. Surface hardness : 8~9H : Three times stronger than regular PET film. Even sharp objects such as knives and keys will not scratch the Glass Screen Protector. Oleophobic Coating : The Glass Screen Protector has an oleophobic coating that prevents fingerprints and other contaminants and makes the film easy to clean. Anti-Shatter Film : If broken, the Glass Screen Protector cracks into small pieces that are held within the film. They are not sharp, making it safer than other glass products. CAUTION *When removing for re-use, the adhesive properties might wear off to an extent where the screen protector will not adhere to the device. It is not recommended to reuse the Glass Screen Protector once it's been applied. *Using excessive force when installing or removing the screen protector may damage the product.
